                                    nr. 205, bl. 254-255.</biblScope> Reykjavík 1909-1913.</bibl> 
                            <bibl><ref type="primary-1" target="EA-A7">Islandske Originaldiplomer indtil 1450: Tekst, nr. 40A, bls. 46–47</ref>.</bibl>
                        </msItem>
                        
